nodes.name: L-histidine:beta-alanine ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + L-Histidine + beta-Alanine <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + Carnosine

nodes.name: Imidazole acetaldehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Imidazole-4-acetaldehyde + NAD+ + H2O <=> Imidazole-4-acetate + NADH + H+

nodes.name: N-methylhistamine:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: N-Methylhistamine + H2O + Oxygen <=> Methylimidazole acetaldehyde + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: 3-Methylimidazole acetaldehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Methylimidazole acetaldehyde + NAD+ + H2O <=> Methylimidazoleacetic acid + NADH + H+

nodes.name: 1H-Imidazole-4-ethanamine:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating) (copper-containing)
nodes.rxn: Histamine + Oxygen + H2O <=> Imidazole-4-acetaldehyde + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: L-histidinal:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: L-Histidinal + H2O + NAD+ <=> L-Histidine + NADH + H+

nodes.name: N(pi)-methyl-L-histidine:beta-alanine ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + N(pi)-Methyl-L-histidine + beta-Alanine <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + beta-Alanyl-N(pi)-methyl-L-histidine

nodes.name: S-(hercyn-2-yl)-L-cysteine-S-oxide ergothioneine-lyase (deaminating
nodes.rxn: S-(Hercyn-2-yl)-L-cysteine S-oxide + Reduced acceptor <=> Ergothioneine + Pyruvate + Ammonia + Acceptor

nodes.name: hercynine,L-cysteine:oxygen [S-(hercyn-2-yl)-L-cysteine S-oxide-forming]
nodes.rxn: Hercynine + L-Cysteine + Oxygen <=> S-(Hercyn-2-yl)-L-cysteine S-oxide + H2O
